 <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">someFinalComputation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"참고 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.yes24.com/Product/Goods/89649360\">리팩터링 2판 책</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#101-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EB%AC%B8-%EB%B6%84%ED%95%B4%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">10.1 조건문 분해하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%A0%88%EC%B0%A8\">절차</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\">예시</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#102-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EC%8B%9D-%ED%86%B5%ED%95%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">10.2 조건식 통합하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%A0%88%EC%B0%A8-1\">절차</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C-or-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">예시: or 사용하기</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#103-%EC%A4%91%EC%B2%A9-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EB%AC%B8%EC%9D%84-%EB%B3%B4%ED%98%B8-%EA%B5%AC%EB%AC%B8%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B0%94%EA%BE%B8%EA%B8%B0\">10.3 중첩 조건문을 보호 구문으로 바꾸기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%A0%88%EC%B0%A8-2\">절차</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C-1\">예시</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\">참고</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"October 0